See the England Births and Christenings listed below which indicate he was born and christened in Liverpool.  LDS Church records in Woolwich, Kent, England indicate that he was born in Liverpool and emigrated in 1856 which is consistent with joining the Martin Handcart Company.  The 1851 census also says he was born in Liverpool.  There are many John Griffiths in Wales and England but to me the evidence listed in the records point to this John has being born in Liverpool.
